Recommended citation:

  Fourie, J., Inwood, K. and Mariotti, M. (2026). Replication data for
  "Discrimination After Hiring: Within-Firm Sorting, Slow Employer Learning,
  and the Cost to the Sorted Worker." github.com/johanfourieza/research,
  2026_sac/.

The data in this package were derived from the South African Constabulary
enlistment registers originally compiled for:

  Fourie, J., Grundlingh, A. and Mariotti, M. (2017). "'Poor South Africa!
  Will no nice English people ever come out here?' The South African
  Constabulary of the Anglo-Boer War." Journal of Imperial and Commonwealth
  History 45 (4): 580-606.

The raw archival transcriptions remain subject to the National Archives of
South Africa's conditions on reuse and are not redistributed here.
